>> servings: 2

Prepare @garlic and smack them, cut @ginger into slices, @spring onions{} into pieces, @chilli into slices.

Add ginger and spring onions to a hot pot and saute till the aroma comes out. Then add @shrimp{6} and saute until both sides are red.

Add @beer{1%can} into the pot and wait till it boils. Add the chilli. Simmer for some time and adjust seasoning with salt.

Serve with cold beer.
